    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/d69326014df7b290a4c720c7ac4ab091.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/d69326014df7b290a4c720c7ac4ab091.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/d69326014df7b290a4c720c7ac4ab091.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>想念一个既不重复又有精彩故事情节和创新游戏机制的经典线性体验吗？《时间融合：卷一 - 女巫与火刑柱》可能是适合你的游戏！你可以在下午5点（单人或与朋友一同）开始进行故事模式，边享用披萨边游戏，一直玩到凌晨3点，完美的游戏之夜！此外，还有另外10小时的挑战模式游戏时间等着你！<br><br>《时间融合》由《月夜惊魂：狼人传说》的联合设计师创作，带你进入一个神秘的梦与噩梦交织的土地，在那里，女巫审判似乎是对抗威胁土地的超自然力量的唯一答案。<br><br>《时间融合》是一款策略冒险游戏，采用独特的游戏机制：时间旅行，玩家可以回到过去与自己一起战斗。你将扮演Teagan，一个女巫，她的力量是最近被一位不受欢迎的客人释放出来的。现在，你必须勇敢前行，拼尽全力净化乡间，摆脱正在腐化着土地的邪恶。<br><br>这不是一款角色扮演游戏（虽然它具备一些我们通常在RPG中看到的特点，如技能树、精彩的故事情节和诡异的配乐），也不是一个开放世界（尽管我们有一场包含20个巨大而独特地图的战役），它真正是一款混合了策略和动作以及各种其他游戏机制（塔防、解谜、首领战、生存任务、护送任务等）的游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/ce868ff8745aa861e978a819cba70f2e.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/ce868ff8745aa861e978a819cba70f2e.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/ce868ff8745aa861e978a819cba70f2e.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点：</h2><br>独特的时间位移游戏机制：以完全确定性的方式倒回时间，与自己一起战斗，而不是由人工智能控制。制定真正定制的策略，按照自己的风格玩游戏！在单人游戏中体验合作游戏机制（仇恨、支援等）！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/801a29b537ec3f16370670b2b173ae4b.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/801a29b537ec3f16370670b2b173ae4b.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/801a29b537ec3f16370670b2b173ae4b.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>混合动作策略玩法：制定策略并实时执行，跨越20多个独特任务！每个任务都有不同的目标，为时间旅行机制带来独特的扭曲！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/d4695d0bdc35f3065bcd687bf6a87f93.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/d4695d0bdc35f3065bcd687bf6a87f93.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/d4695d0bdc35f3065bcd687bf6a87f93.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>合作模式：与在线上的朋友一同进行完整的战役（2名玩家）！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/99202ca481e9308f586e8a48eb32a158.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/99202ca481e9308f586e8a48eb32a158.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/99202ca481e9308f586e8a48eb32a158.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>引人注目的故事情节：引人入胜的战役，带给你各种扭转、曲折、隐秘和令人瞠目结舌的时光旅行故事！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/51f224c5d2266b7bea689ef28bfc3838.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/51f224c5d2266b7bea689ef28bfc3838.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/51f224c5d2266b7bea689ef28bfc3838.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>挑战模式：通过40个让人思维缜密、需要四维思考的挑战测试你的脑力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/0eff18a97de6f5c572e428ad0538ddf9.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/0eff18a97de6f5c572e428ad0538ddf9.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/0eff18a97de6f5c572e428ad0538ddf9.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>技能树：选择如何升级你的法术，获得越来越强大的魔法和复杂的构建选择！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/ed51ab2dae0bdd3c4f27169810231ee9.poster.avif?t=1758409892\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/ed51ab2dae0bdd3c4f27169810231ee9.webm?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096140/extras/ed51ab2dae0bdd3c4f27169810231ee9.mp4?t=1758409892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>原声音轨：富丽堂皇、宏大的原声音轨，充满史诗般的时刻（以及一些让人难以忘怀的旋律）！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为什么制作这款游戏？</h2><br>首先，我们尽力制作我们自己想玩的游戏。随着年龄的增长，我们并不总是有很多空闲时间，在一天中可能只有零星的30分钟可以用来游戏。因此，我们想创造一些能让你迅速投入行动的东西。没有频繁的更新、长时间的加载时间或疯狂的菜单管理。这款游戏适合那些想要立即体验策略和激烈动作的人，同时配备一个技能系统以增加变化，并拥有精彩的故事情节。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >期待什么：</h2><br>我们是一个由3个人组成的小团队，花了我们5年时间制作这款游戏。虽然我们都是经验丰富且热情洋溢的开发人员，但请不要期望AAA级的图形。然而，你可以期待前所未见的游戏机制和创新系统。因为《时间融合》在切割边缘图形方面可能有所欠缺，但却以其独特的设计和引人入胜的叙事弥补了这一点！<br><br>无论如何，我们希望你会像我们一样热爱《时间融合》！祝你游戏愉快！",
